name: Emma Buckland's Homepage
tagline: Emma Buckland will probably have her own website one day. Until then, her Daddy will have to build one for her.
body:
### Welcome to Emma's Site.
Emma is still very small, and doesn't know what code is yet. But she is learning how to build other stuff, and already knows how to break things, so she'll be great when she gets round to it.

Her [Daddy](https://github.com/alexbuckland) maintains this for now.
___
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
